title: Dark Star Icons....
body:
A while back, I started playing the dark star game mode for quite a few games, won many and lost many, (I played on the 13 and the deadline was the 15) I did play with my friends and got a total of more than 33 kills.  Is there any reason I wouldn't have it by now?  {{champion:32}} 

_** Dark Star: Singularity runs from 5/4/2017 at 11 AM PT to 5/15/2017 at 11:59 PM PT**_

Here's a screenshot
https://gyazo.com/83726275578aa51d9ca73678a214dd32

replies.body: Don't worry just yet! That Dark Star event page also states that the icons will be going out until 5/29. If you don't have it by 5/29, at that point you can hit us up in a ticket to get it taken care of ^_^!
If you go to the site, it says that the icons should be on your account by the 29th.
